### Hyland Document Management Service - API Tests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001/api
@devBaseUrl = http://localhost:5214/api
@contentType = application/json

### Swagger UI (Development)
GET http://localhost:5214/swagger
Accept: text/html

### OpenAPI Specification (Development)  
GET http://localhost:5214/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

### Home Page (redirects to OpenAPI)
GET http://localhost:5214/
Accept: application/json

### Get Query Metering Status
GET {{devBaseUrl}}/hylanddocuments/query-metering/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Configure Query Metering
POST {{devBaseUrl}}/hylanddocuments/query-metering/configure
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "maxQueriesPerHour": 1500,
  "warningThreshold": 85
}

###

### Get All Documents (Hyland)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Document (Hyland)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create New Document (Hyland)
POST {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fileName": "test-doc.pdf",
  "fileType": "Legal Contract",
  "fileSizeBytes": 1024768,
  "contentType": "application/pdf",
  "description": "Test document for Hyland integration",
  "uploadedBy": "api-user",
  "metadata": {
    "Department": "Legal",
    "Category": "Contract",
    "Priority": "High",
    "Confidential": "true"
  }
}

###

### Update Document (Hyland)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "Updated description for testing",
  "metadata": {
    "Department": "Legal",
    "Category": "Updated Contract",
    "Priority": "Medium",
    "LastReviewed": "2026-01-31"
  },
  "status": "InReview"
}

###

### Search Documents (Hyland)
POST {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments/search
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fileType": "Legal Contract",
  "uploadedFrom": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "uploadedTo": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "status": "Active",
  "metadata": {
    "Department": "Legal",
    "Category": "Contract"
  }
}

###

### Archive Document (Hyland)
POST {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments/1/archive
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Get Document Content (Hyland)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments/1/content
Accept: application/octet-stream

###

### Delete Document (Hyland)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments/1

###

### Legacy Endpoints (for backward compatibility)
### Get All Documents (Legacy)
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Query Limit (Execute multiple requests to test metering)
### First request
GET {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments

###

### Second request
GET {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments

###

### Third request
GET {{baseUrl}}/hylanddocuments

###